text:
[Verse]
Stars are shining bright
In the still of night
Moon is casting light
Everything feels right

[Verse 2]
Cool breeze in my hair
No worries no care
Walk without a fear
Wishes fill the air

[Chorus]
Under the midnight sky
We just laugh we just fly
Dreams that never die
You and I so high

[Verse 3]
Humming to a tune
By the silver moon
With you time feels soon
Heart in perfect tune

[Verse 4]
City lights afar
Blinking like a star
Feel the beat from the car
You play your guitar

[Chorus]
Under the midnight sky
We just laugh we just fly
Dreams that never die
You and I so high
title: Under the Midnight Sky
